OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777036267
OL,3,CGroundbreaking surgery carried out on
OL,4,Cteenager using blood from more than 100
OL,6,FA teenager has undergone
OL,7,Fgroundbreaking surgery to remove a
OL,8,Fbrain tumour which involved blood
OL,9,Fdonations from more than 100 people.
OL,11,FAhmed Khan lives with an extremely
OL,12,Frare blood disorder and was told he
OL,13,Fneeded to have the tumour removed if
OL,14,Fhe wanted to live.
OL,16,FThe 17-year-old however faced further
OL,17,Frisk in the surgery from chances of
OL,18,Fhuge blood loss due to living with
OL,19,FBernard-Soulier Syndrome, an inherited
OL,20,Fcondition which inhibits the body's
OL,21,Fability for the blood to clot.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
