OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777036267
OL,3,CGroundbreaking surgery carried out on
OL,4,Cteenager using blood from more than 100
OL,6,FAhmed, from Sheffield, underwent the
OL,7,F13-hour operation at Sheffield
OL,8,FChildren's Hospital using a range of
OL,9,Fblood components from 113 different
OL,10,Fdonors.
OL,12,FHe was diagnosed with a pineal brain
OL,13,Ftumour after noticing double vision
OL,14,Fback in May 2023. Doctors told the
OL,15,Ffamily that he wouldn't live without
OL,16,Fsurgery, but that the operation also
OL,17,Fcarried huge risk of death because of
OL,18,Fthe condition he was diagnosed with as
OL,19,Fa newborn.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777036267
OL,3,CGroundbreaking surgery carried out on
OL,4,Cteenager using blood from more than 100
OL,6,FHis mother, Maryam Bilal, a nurse,
OL,7,Fsaid: "You never think you are going
OL,8,Fto be told that your teenage son has
OL,9,Fcancer. You always think it happens to
OL,10,Fother people, not you. The whole world
OL,11,Fjust came crashing down around us."
OL,13,FChemotherapy was not enough to stop
OL,14,Fthe tumour's growth, while Ahmed also
OL,15,Fdeveloped antibodies from previous
OL,16,Fplatelet transfusions - meaning they
OL,17,Fwould no longer work.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@cO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777036267
OL,3,CGroundbreaking surgery carried out on
OL,4,Cteenager using blood from more than 100
OL,6,FThe hospital, which is this year
OL,7,Fcelebrating its 150-year anniversary,
OL,8,Fsays Ahmed's surgery was a result of
OL,9,Fmeticulous planning between doctors
OL,10,Fand colleagues from NHS Blood and
OL,11,FTransplant (NHSBT).
OL,13,FConsultant neurosurgeon Veejay Bagga,
OL,14,Fwho led the surgery, said: "If we did
OL,15,Fnothing, the tumour would have been
OL,16,Ffatal."
OL,18,FThe surgery has since been hailed a
OL,19,Fsuccess, with Ahmed's recovery going
OL,20,Fso well he has even taken up running.
OL,26,@vD@\OU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777036267
OL,3,CGroundbreaking surgery carried out on
OL,4,Cteenager using blood from more than 100
OL,6,FThe teenager, who is doing T-levels in
OL,7,Fmechanical engineering at college,
OL,8,Fsaid he "wouldn't be here today"
OL,9,Fwithout staff's skill and dedication.
OL,11,F"They gave me a chance to continue my
OL,12,Flife and look forward to the future."
OL,14,FBernard-Soulier is an extremely rare
OL,15,Fcondition affecting fewer than 100
OL,16,Fpeople in the UK.
OL,18,FMaryam said: "We had never heard of it
OL,19,Fbefore. We were told the chances of
OL,20,Fhaving it were more than a million to
OL,21,Fone.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@eO]zD@NOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777036267
OL,3,CGroundbreaking surgery carried out on
OL,4,Cteenager using blood from more than 100
OL,6,F"We have always had to be careful.
OL,7,FFrom the start we were told that
OL,8,Fsurgery could carry a risk of death
OL,9,Fbecause his blood might not clot
OL,10,Fproperly."
OL,12,FThe condition meant he would need
OL,13,Fplasma exchange treatment in the week
OL,14,Fbefore his surgery to reduce
OL,15,Fantibodies.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
