FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777036267
OL,3,CGroundbreaking surgery carried out on
OL,4,Cteenager using blood from more than 100
OL,6,FDonations had to be carefully vetted
OL,7,Fand matched to his tissue type to
OL,8,Fprevent his immune system rejecting
OL,9,Fthem, while Ahmed's minority ethnic
OL,10,Fbackground meant it would be harder to
OL,11,Ffind close matches due to
OL,12,Funderrepresentation in the donor base.
OL,14,FConsultant neurosurgeon Veejay Bagga,
OL,15,Fwho led the surgery, said: "If we did
OL,16,Fnothing, the tumour would have been
OL,17,Ffatal."
OL,26,@wD@\OU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
