FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1777036267
OL,3,CGroundbreaking surgery carried out on
OL,4,Cteenager using blood from more than 100
OL,6,FConsultant haematologist Jeanette
OL,7,FPayne, who co-ordinated the complex
OL,8,Fblood management plan, said: "I have
OL,9,Flooked after Ahmed since diagnosing
OL,10,Fhis condition when he was a baby.
OL,12,F"When he developed a brain tumour as a
OL,13,Fteenager it was incredibly worrying
OL,14,Fbecause treating cancer in someone
OL,15,Fwith a severe bleeding disorder is
OL,16,Fextremely challenging."
OL,26,@pD@^OUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
